Noddy, Big-Ears Owner Chorion May Hire Banks for Shake-Up, Sky News Says

-- B y   M a r i a   E r m a k o v a
-- 
2011-03-17T13:16:48Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-17/noddy-big-ears-owner-chorion-may-hire-banks-for-shake-up-sky-news-says.html
Chorion, the owner of children
characters such as Noddy and Big-Ears, may hire DC Advisory
Partners Ltd. to assess options that may include one of the
shareholders  3i Group Plc (III)  cutting its stake or selling its
holding, Sky News’s Mark Kleinman reported, citing unidentified
bankers.     Walt Disney Co. (DIS) , Mattel, Inc. and Viacom Inc.’s Nickelodeon
unit are interested in buying the character Thomas the Tank
Engine, which may be sold separately, according to Kleinman.    To contact the editor responsible for this story:
